@@TJvCustomValidateEdit
Summary
  Edit control that can restrict it's content to only accept valid input.
Description
  TJvCustomValidateEdit is a base class for edit controls that can restrict user input and format
  it's content. To put a validating edit control on a form, don't use TJvCustomValidateEdit.
  Instead, use a derived component like TJvValidateEdit.
