@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.AsCurrency
Summary
  Represents the Text property as a Currency value.
Description
  Use AsCurrency to read the value of the Text property into an object or variable of type Currency
  or to assign a Currency value to the Text property.
Note
  If the current value of Text cannot be represented as a currency value, AsCurrency returns 0.
