@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.Assign
Summary
  Copies the properties of another instance to this object.
Description
  Use Assign to copy the properties of another TJvCustomValidateEdit (or descendant) to this object.
  The properties copied are CriticalPoints, DisplayFormat, DecimalPlaces, MinValue, MaxValue,
  HasMinValue, HasMaxValue and ZeroEmpty.

  If Source is not derived from TJvCustomValidateEdit, Assign calls inherited Assign.
Parameters
  Source - The object to copy from.
