@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.AutoAlignment
Summary
  Specifies if alignment is changed automatically.
Description
  Use AutoAlignment to specify if the alignmnt of the text is automatically changed when the
  DisplayFormat is changed. If AutoAlignment is True, DisplayFormat's that are numeric in
  nature are right-justified and all others are left-justified. Set AutoAlignment to False to
  control the Alignment manually.
See Also
  DisplayFormat, Alignment
